import sys

n = int(sys.stdin.readline().strip())
x = list(map(int, sys.stdin.readline().strip().split()))
y = list(map(int, sys.stdin.readline().strip().split()))

for i in range(n):
    if x[i] != y[i]:
        print("No")
        sys.exit(0)

print("Yes")
